text: The following is a list of notable events and releases of the year 1885 in Norwegian music. ==Events== ==Deaths== ==Births== ; October * 15 – Fridtjof Backer-Grøndahl, pianist, composer and music teacher (died 1959). ; November * 14 – Trygve Torjussen, pianist and composer (died 1977). ; December * 6 – Helge Klæstad, Supreme Court judge and composer (died 1965). ==See also== * 1885 in Norway * Music of Norway ==References== Category:Norwegian music Norwegian Music Category:1880s in Norwegian music
